WEBVTT

01:27:10.649 --> 01:27:12.483
I need to find out
what Sahadevan is after.

01:27:12.566 --> 01:27:15.191
If he starts stirring things up,
that'll be our next headache.

01:27:16.024 --> 01:27:17.899
The media had more or less
forgotten about it.

01:27:18.691 --> 01:27:20.149
I don't think so, sir.
